headline: KEY FAMILY WEALTH WINS 'BEST EDUCATIONAL INITIATIVE' AWARD AT THE 2026 PRIVATE ASSET MANAGEMENT AWARDS
summary: Key Family Wealth, the multi-family office division of KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY), was awarded "Best Educational Initiative" at the Private Asset Management (PAM) Awards in New York City from a distinguished list of wealth management competitors.
